name: SearchResponse.Links
desc: See the links returned by the search article endpoints.

items.name: self
items.desc: The URL for the current page of search results.

items.name: next
items.desc: The URL for the next page of search results. If next is null, there are no more pages. The next link may occasionally return an empty page of results (if, for example, an article in the original set of search results has been deleted since the results were obtained).
